		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a tiny utility for Windows XP that lets you use Windows Key + Left/Right to make a window fill the left half or right half of the screen, just like in Windows 7.<br />The executable is 2kb in size.  No bloat here.<br /><a href="http://www.dwedit.org/dwedit_board/attachment.php?item=378" class="postlink">Download</a><br /><a href="http://www.dwedit.org/dwedit_board/attachment.php?item=379" class="postlink">Source Code</a>

		

